{"tid":967482,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人一專注就會頭暈頭痛？","createTime":"2019-01-03T13:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T19:45:01.000Z","uid":90663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc9c03f57c660197389c918acbaa7c16fb3045f","tid":967482,"uid":90663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:48:17.000Z","msg":"成日好專注做緊一件事就會成身唔舒服<br />\n好似發燒咁好熱<br />\n之後會好似暈車浪咁想嘔、頭痛、頭暈咁<br />\n好多時都維持一段長時間先無野<br />\n有無巴絲係咁？<br />\n好困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e753cdf76c40bfdf5bea42d54feae390188a3c0","tid":967482,"uid":225679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:51:24.000Z","msg":"我都係成日偏頭痛<br />\n睇過好多醫生 照x死光都冇野<br />\n醫生多數係壓力 緊張 令到血加速<br />\n頭痛咁形成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fed1dbc1eab86a35572b5fa5d4ba37c044d952c","tid":967482,"uid":224107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"做野太集中係容易會有偏頭痛<br />\n<br />\n利申：之前返緊工經常偏頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34abd7d8cf9dd85458c30c0dd4fc813c47dd30f9","tid":967482,"uid":47850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T12:04:56.000Z","msg":"我係一搵嘢執嘢就頭痛"},{"pid":"b83ae0f2ff4548c60ffa098467bb457e026df913","tid":967482,"uid":44180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T12:56:39.000Z","msg":"我通常有緊急既野要搞 環境有d焗 空氣唔流通<br />\n又要對住電腦mon d字又細粒 <br />\n個人會浮下浮下 心跌得快左咁"},{"pid":"5e50a90ef7f1592e68824bfc57c3f5dd7e42c02c","tid":967482,"uid":7306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T19:45:01.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n成日諗呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n對住電話好多個鐘個頭都唔會痛<br />\n<br />\n做其他嘢一專心就頭痛"}]}